title: Pedro Aguilera - La Influencia (2007)
description:
Pedro Aguilera's film about a woman unable to cope
and the effects of her decline on her children.

Not a bad film, it is Aguilera's first as a director (he was an assistant director on "Sangre" and "Batalla en el Cielo").

I had trouble conecting to, downloading and seeding the existing torrents; so once I had eventually downloaded the film I thought I would start this new torrent.

I can find no subtitles for this Spanish language film,
however the film is almost silent and it can be
understood perfectly well without them.
